         <abstract id="aspace_f56bb4b95d3cfd8fa4bcfa852ec9de2f">Collection features early sketches by Louis I. Kahn of the Yale Center for British Art building.  This includes exterior elevations, interior and exterior renderings, and floor plans.</abstract>
